{
  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "This absolute value (no implied physical meaning) is simply a means of triggering events.",
    "Conventional frequency filtering is not applied during pre-processing in order to maintain the full range of frequencies available to be captured by the multi-STA/LTA algorithm.",
    "We compile a cryoseismic event catalogue for the WIS using the multi-STA/LTA algorithm with optimized parameters as outlined above (Sect. 2.2).",
    "We use the waveform handling pipeline for automated analysis developed by Turner et al. (2021a), adding the multi-STA/LTA as a new option, with a view to subsequent signal reconnaissance using unsupervised learning (Part 2, Latto et al., 2024).",
    "We apply a trigger value of 3 and a detrigger value of 1, chosen as a set of triggers that effectively produce a catalogue that includes a sensible number of events."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "We use the waveform handling pipeline for automated analysis developed by Turner et al. (2021a), adding the multi-STA/LTA as a new option, with a view to subsequent signal reconnaissance using unsupervised learning (Part 2, Latto et al., 2024)."
